any carbon dioxide and the fact

00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:52.270 align:middle line:10%
that it is not intermittent,
unlike the sun or the wind,

00:13:52.270 --> 00:13:54.520 align:middle line:10%
all these factors
combined together

00:13:54.520 --> 00:13:58.840 align:middle line:10%
led to calling fusion
